div.div: The third season of Shingeki no Kyojin. Eren and his companions in the 104th are assigned to the newly-formed Levi Squad, whose assignment is to keep Eren and Historia safe given Eren's newly-discovered power and Historia's knowledge and pedigree. Levi and Erwin have good reason to be concerned, because the priest of the Church that Hanji had hidden away was found tortured to death, making it clear that the Military Police are involved with the cover-up. Things get more harrowing when the MPs make a move on Erwin and the Levi Squad narrowly avoids capture. Eren is also having problems with his Titan transformation, and a deadly killer has been hired to secure Eren and Historia, one Levi knows all too well from his youth. (Source: Anime News Network)
Action, Drama, Mecha, Psychological, Romance, Sci-Fi

Tokyo 2039, Japan has fallen under the control of the multinational organization GHQ after the outbreak, in 2029, of an epidemic caused by a virus known as Apocalypse.
Shuu Ouma, wielder of "The Power of Kings", has led a rather secluded life at least until his encounter with Gai Tsusugami and Yuzuriha Inori, members of the resistance, thrusts him into the fight against the GHQ.

Young Asta was born with no magic ability in a world where magic is everything. In order to prove his strength and keep a promise with his friend, Asta dreams of becoming the greatest mage in the land, the Wizard King!
(Source: Viz Media)
Drama, Fantasy, Horror, Mystery, Psychological, Thriller

Emma, Norman and Ray are the brightest kids at the Grace Field House orphanage. And under the care of the woman they refer to as Mom, all the kids have enjoyed a comfortable life. Good food, clean clothes and the perfect environment to learnwhat more could an orphan ask for? One day, though, Emma and Norman uncover the dark truth of the outside world they are forbidden from seeing. (Source: Viz Media) Note: Nominated to the 22nd, 23rd, and 25th Annual Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize.
